[Amit Varma]: is great numbers, advertisers haven't really woken up to the insane engagement level of

00:05:20.280 --> 00:05:25.760
[Amit Varma]: podcasts. I do many, many hours of deep research for each episode. Besides all the logistics

00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:31.880
[Amit Varma]: of producing the show myself, scheduling guests, booking studios, paying technicians, the travel

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:36.960
[Amit Varma]: and so on. So well, I'm trying a new way of keeping this thing going. And that involves

