[Amit Varma]: is stellar, but so is a local collection. They have a fantastic range of Marathi and

00:35:38.400 --> 00:35:43.640
[Amit Varma]: Hindi audio books. What's more, I do a weekly podcast there called the book club with Amit

00:35:43.640 --> 00:35:48.360
[Amit Varma]: Verma, in which I talk about one book every week, giving context, giving you a taste of

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:53.880
[Amit Varma]: it and so on. Download that app and listen to my show. And as long as Storytel sponsors

00:35:53.880 --> 00:35:58.360
[Amit Varma]: this show within this commercial itself, I will recommend an audio book that I liked

00:35:58.360 --> 00:36:04.920
[Amit Varma]: on that platform every week. My recommendation for this week is Mitro Marjani by Krishna

